.TH JITML 1
.SH NAME
jitml \- deterministic, reproducible, JIT-compiled machine learning
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B jitml
COMMAND [OPTIONS]
.SH DESCRIPTION
The jitml command surface is generated from the CommandSpec registry.
.SH COMMANDS
.SS JITML BOOTSTRAP
Bootstrap a substrate stack.
.PP
.B jitml bootstrap [\\-\\-apple\\-silicon] [\\-\\-linux\\-cpu] [\\-\\-linux\\-cuda] [\\-\\-dry\\-run] [\\-\\-plan\\-file <path>]
.SS JITML DOCTOR
Check host prerequisites.
.PP
.B jitml doctor [\\-\\-scope <toolchain|container|cluster>] [\\-\\-remediate]
.SS JITML SERVICE
Run the jitML daemon.
.PP
.B jitml service [\\-\\-config <path>] [\\-\\-consume\\-once <n>] [\\-\\-dry\\-run] [\\-\\-plan\\-file <path>]
.SS JITML CLUSTER UP
Bring the cluster up.
.PP
.B jitml cluster up [\\-\\-substrate <substrate>] [\\-\\-dry\\-run] [\\-\\-plan\\-file <path>]
.SS JITML CLUSTER DOWN
Bring the cluster down.
.PP
.B jitml cluster down
.SS JITML CLUSTER STATUS
Report cluster status.
.PP
.B jitml cluster status
.SS JITML CLUSTER RESET
Destructively reset cluster state.
.PP
.B jitml cluster reset \\-\\-yes
.SS JITML TRAIN
Run a supervised training job.
.PP
.B jitml train <experiment\\-dhall> [\\-\\-resume <checkpoint\\-id>] [\\-\\-substrate <substrate>] [\\-\\-seed <word64>] [\\-\\-dry\\-run] [\\-\\-plan\\-file <path>]
.SS JITML EVAL
Run deterministic evaluation.
.PP
.B jitml eval <experiment\\-dhall> [\\-\\-checkpoint <checkpoint\\-id>]
.SS JITML TUNE
Run a hyperparameter sweep.
.PP
.B jitml tune <tune\\-dhall> [\\-\\-resume <sweep\\-id>] [\\-\\-sampler <name>] [\\-\\-scheduler <name>] [\\-\\-pruner <name>] [\\-\\-trials <natural>] [\\-\\-parallelism <natural>] [\\-\\-dry\\-run] [\\-\\-plan\\-file <path>]
.SS JITML RL TRAIN
Train an RL policy.
.PP
.B jitml rl train <rl\\-experiment\\-dhall> [\\-\\-resume <checkpoint\\-id>] [\\-\\-substrate <substrate>] [\\-\\-seed <word64>] [\\-\\-dry\\-run] [\\-\\-plan\\-file <path>]
.SS JITML RL EVAL
Evaluate an RL policy.
.PP
.B jitml rl eval <rl\\-experiment\\-dhall> [\\-\\-checkpoint <checkpoint\\-id>]
.SS JITML RL ROLLOUT
Run a fixed\\-seed rollout.
.PP
.B jitml rl rollout <rl\\-experiment\\-dhall> [\\-\\-seed <word64>]
.SS JITML RL ALPHAZERO SELF-PLAY
Run AlphaZero self\\-play.
.PP
.B jitml rl alphazero self\\-play [\\-\\-substrate <substrate>] [\\-\\-seed <word64>] [\\-\\-games <n>] [\\-\\-sims <n>] [\\-\\-max\\-plies <n>] [\\-\\-updates <n>] [\\-\\-arena\\-games <n>]
.SS JITML VERIFY SAME-RUN
Verify same\\-run determinism.
.PP
.B jitml verify same\\-run \\-\\-experiment <experiment\\-dhall> \\-\\-runs <int>
.SS JITML VERIFY REPLAY
Verify checkpoint replay.
.PP
.B jitml verify replay \\-\\-experiment <experiment\\-dhall> \\-\\-checkpoint <checkpoint\\-id>
.SS JITML INSPECT LIST
List cached manifests.
.PP
.B jitml inspect list
.SS JITML INSPECT SHOW
Show a manifest.
.PP
.B jitml inspect show <manifest\\-sha> [\\-\\-with\\-equity]
.SS JITML INSPECT REPLAY
Replay a manifest.
.PP
.B jitml inspect replay [<manifest\\-sha>] [\\-\\-manifest\\-sha <manifest\\-sha>] [\\-\\-experiment\\-hash <experiment\\-hash>]
.SS JITML INSPECT TRIAL
Inspect a trial.
.PP
.B jitml inspect trial <trial\\-hash>
.SS JITML INSPECT FRONTIER
Inspect a tuning frontier.
.PP
.B jitml inspect frontier <sweep\\-id>
.SS JITML BENCH TRAIN
Benchmark training.
.PP
.B jitml bench train <experiment\\-dhall>
.SS JITML BENCH INFERENCE
Benchmark inference.
.PP
.B jitml bench inference <experiment\\-dhall> \\-\\-checkpoint <checkpoint\\-id>
.SS JITML BENCH ENV
Benchmark environment stepping.
.PP
.B jitml bench env <rl\\-experiment\\-dhall>
.SS JITML INFERENCE RUN
Run inference at any point.
.PP
.B jitml inference run [<experiment\\-dhall>] [\\-\\-checkpoint <latest|best/<metric>|manifest\\-sha>] [\\-\\-trial <trial\\-hash>] [\\-\\-experiment\\-hash <experiment\\-hash>]
.SS JITML TEST ALL
Run all test stanzas.
.PP
.B jitml test all [\\-\\-live] [\\-\\-apple\\-silicon] [\\-\\-linux\\-cpu] [\\-\\-linux\\-cuda] [\\-\\-test\\-options <text>] [\\-\\-dry\\-run] [\\-\\-plan\\-file <path>]
.SS JITML TEST JITML-UNIT
Run jitml\\-unit.
.PP
.B jitml test jitml\\-unit [\\-\\-apple\\-silicon] [\\-\\-linux\\-cpu] [\\-\\-linux\\-cuda] [\\-\\-test\\-options <text>]
.SS JITML TEST JITML-INTEGRATION
Run jitml\\-integration.
.PP
.B jitml test jitml\\-integration [\\-\\-apple\\-silicon] [\\-\\-linux\\-cpu] [\\-\\-linux\\-cuda] [\\-\\-test\\-options <text>]
.SS JITML TEST JITML-SL-CANONICALS
Run jitml\\-sl\\-canonicals.
.PP
.B jitml test jitml\\-sl\\-canonicals [\\-\\-apple\\-silicon] [\\-\\-linux\\-cpu] [\\-\\-linux\\-cuda] [\\-\\-test\\-options <text>]
.SS JITML TEST JITML-RL-CANONICALS
Run jitml\\-rl\\-canonicals.
.PP
.B jitml test jitml\\-rl\\-canonicals [\\-\\-apple\\-silicon] [\\-\\-linux\\-cpu] [\\-\\-linux\\-cuda] [\\-\\-test\\-options <text>]
.SS JITML TEST JITML-HYPERPARAMETER
Run jitml\\-hyperparameter.
.PP
.B jitml test jitml\\-hyperparameter [\\-\\-apple\\-silicon] [\\-\\-linux\\-cpu] [\\-\\-linux\\-cuda] [\\-\\-test\\-options <text>]
.SS JITML TEST JITML-BACKENDS
Run jitml\\-backends.
.PP
.B jitml test jitml\\-backends [\\-\\-apple\\-silicon] [\\-\\-linux\\-cpu] [\\-\\-linux\\-cuda] [\\-\\-test\\-options <text>]
.SS JITML TEST JITML-DAEMON-LIFECYCLE
Run jitml\\-daemon\\-lifecycle.
.PP
.B jitml test jitml\\-daemon\\-lifecycle [\\-\\-apple\\-silicon] [\\-\\-linux\\-cpu] [\\-\\-linux\\-cuda] [\\-\\-test\\-options <text>]
.SS JITML TEST JITML-E2E
Run jitml\\-e2e.
.PP
.B jitml test jitml\\-e2e [\\-\\-apple\\-silicon] [\\-\\-linux\\-cpu] [\\-\\-linux\\-cuda] [\\-\\-test\\-options <text>]
.SS JITML LINT FILES
Run file hygiene checks.
.PP
.B jitml lint files [\\-\\-write]
.SS JITML LINT DOCS
Run generated documentation checks.
.PP
.B jitml lint docs [\\-\\-write]
.SS JITML LINT PROTO
Run protobuf schema lint checks.
.PP
.B jitml lint proto [\\-\\-write]
.SS JITML LINT CHART
Run Helm chart shape checks.
.PP
.B jitml lint chart [\\-\\-write]
.SS JITML LINT HASKELL
Run Haskell lint configuration and primitive checks.
.PP
.B jitml lint haskell [\\-\\-write]
.SS JITML LINT PURESCRIPT
Run PureScript contract and format checks.
.PP
.B jitml lint purescript [\\-\\-write]
.SS JITML LINT ALL
Run every currently implemented lint check.
.PP
.B jitml lint all [\\-\\-write]
.SS JITML DOCS CHECK
Check generated docs.
.PP
.B jitml docs check
.SS JITML DOCS GENERATE
Generate docs.
.PP
.B jitml docs generate
.SS JITML CHECK-CODE
Run the code quality gate.
.PP
.B jitml check\\-code
.SS JITML BUILD
Build inside the substrate container.
.PP
.B jitml build [\\-\\-substrate <substrate>] [\\-\\-dry\\-run] [\\-\\-plan\\-file <path>]
.SS JITML KUBECTL
Run kubectl against the jitML kubeconfig.
.PP
.B jitml kubectl [\\-\\- <kubectl\\-args...>]
.SS JITML INTERNAL MATERIALIZE-SUBSTRATE
Materialize substrate files.
.PP
.B jitml internal materialize\\-substrate [\\-\\-substrate <substrate>]
.SS JITML INTERNAL LIST-PREREQS
List prerequisite checks.
.PP
.B jitml internal list\\-prereqs
.SS JITML INTERNAL INSTALL-METAL-BRIDGE
Build the fixed Apple Metal bridge.
.PP
.B jitml internal install\\-metal\\-bridge
.SS JITML INTERNAL UPLOAD-DATASET
Upload a real dataset blob to MinIO.
.PP
.B jitml internal upload\\-dataset [\\-\\-name <name>] [\\-\\-split <split>] [\\-\\-artifact <artifact>] [\\-\\-path <path>] [\\-\\-dry\\-run] [\\-\\-plan\\-file <path>]
.SS JITML INTERNAL GC
Apply checkpoint retention.
.PP
.B jitml internal gc <experiment\\-hash> [\\-\\-dry\\-run] [\\-\\-plan\\-file <path>]
.SS JITML INTERNAL CACHE STAT
Print cache stats.
.PP
.B jitml internal cache stat
.SS JITML INTERNAL CACHE LIST
List cache entries.
.PP
.B jitml internal cache list
.SS JITML INTERNAL CACHE EVICT
Evict a cache entry.
.PP
.B jitml internal cache evict <hash>
.SS JITML COMMANDS
Print the command registry.
.PP
.B jitml commands [\\-\\-tree] [\\-\\-json]
.SS JITML HELP
Print focused command help.
.PP
.B jitml help [\\-\\- <subcommand...>]
